{"tid":2114592,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"想係香港講英文唔比人笑 一定要符合呢d條件","createTime":"2020-07-19T03:07:03.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-19T13:59:57.000Z","uid":52013,"like":45,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"d08987f4f37bee25915ee26f0b440bb52cebbcd9","tid":2114592,"uid":52013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T03:07:03.000Z","msg":"1. Queen English received pronunciation.<br />\n<br />\n連登仔每個都有最正宗既英國皇室口音<br />\n如果唔係呢種口音 你只係一個鄉下仔 同大陸人無咩分別 建議你收口唔好扮野識英文<br />\n<br />\n2. Grammar-mania/nazi<br />\n<br />\nWritten English有Grammar就緊架啦<br />\n但係Conversation English都必須要遵循Grammar rule 必須先修讀Oxford Grammar book 十年先至可以係香港使用英文<br />\n<br />\n3. Guru of Intonation and meaningful English<br />\n<br />\n講野抑揚頓挫 聽到人地出耳油<br />\n媲美頂級演說家 每一句都賺人熱淚 感人肺腑 同 發人深省<br />\n<br />\n4. Various and diverse sentence structure and vocabulary range<br />\n<br />\n用字同句子都力臻完美 必須為 Formal and literary word. 絕對唔會講d通俗 常用英語  講野要出口成文 認為Williams Shakespeare都只係中學雞級數<br />\n<br />\n5. Attitude of using English in HK<br />\n<br />\n呢種心態/風氣係同輩間或網絡上 盛行一時 ---- 屌你 識講或者打中文 無啦啦學咩人講英文 以為自己好叻？懶係野<br />\n無視英語使用者背後原意同抹殺佢既努力<br />\n人地都係想培養Think in English既狀態<br />\n想捉緊每一次使用英文既機會 但熱情往往比呢d人減弱咗<br />\n<br />\n歡迎大家補充更多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"477d485380f10b4ec71ca509f17977f296213256","tid":2114592,"uid":53379,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T03:07:57.000Z","msg":"靚仔/靚女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d21fd603289125931edfc3700b4bb7d5de039652","tid":2114592,"uid":52013,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"477d485380f10b4ec71ca509f17977f296213256","tid":2114592,"uid":53379,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T03:07:57.000Z","msg":"靚仔/靚女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T03:08:17.000Z","msg":"關乜事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\