da07d57861182358952","tid":2114592,"uid":194120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3816d84709296adae62d536462564c42cde34d8f","tid":2114592,"uid":249885,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"e0f43a2003909ae6f8333ffdcab1d88a12fd0434","tid":2114592,"uid":194120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T03:37:58.000Z","msg":"英文最正宗口音好似係Oxford,中學時教英文個呀Sir佢後生喺嗰邊讀書,佢講嘅英文發音同一般聽嘅真係唔同."},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T03:55:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T04:08:41.000Z","msg":"或者佢喺嗰邊成績屎啩？最記得佢作風都好英國，外觀成個呀伯咁，無時無刻都西装打呔，就算大熱天時校運會都係咁着。<br />\n有樣過癮係放咗學一過咗條馬路佢就煲煙，牌子係香港唔太多人食嘅英國金邊臣。"},{"pid":"81b615c18c3fbf7585856371a9587610a713ac9d","tid":2114592,"uid":71459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9b48ffdc61efe3e4db060cd99772342dcfa31acb","tid":2114592,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T03:22:28.000Z","msg":"煙 tern~"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T04:17:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2fwmg2e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2fwmg2e.png&h=ace8d39a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"07edceafffd26b6b0d19dd356b83609b1a0b8ab2","tid":2114592,"uid":71459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"670d8173718789df757be47e7bb7ecaa7599d2c6","tid":2114592,"uid":325421,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T03:38:27.000Z","msg":"其實香港人用返香港人既口音有咩問題？好似印度佬有印度佬口音，你唔會話佢唔識英文掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T04:18:28.000Z","msg":"印度佬都唔識英文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6df1fa95ff9346e6815d55066263d3b829c43ccc","tid":2114592,"uid":308450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T05:53:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0be599ef6bf06c9b8b92d60bd476a08750959705","tid":2114592,"uid":52013,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T06:47:38.000Z","msg":"呢篇文都係抽下水姐<br />\n<br />\n我就覺得鬼佬聽得明 唔洗解謎式理解就okay. （Spoken English）"},{"pid":"b16e143c3d924d942c8f482c439bfbf5a2fea473","tid":2114592,"uid":72173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T06:59:46.000Z","msg":"所以通常writing好過speaking<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a90c4cba845fe842558f994e65f3ad73bd52d368","tid":2114592,"uid":360830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d08987f4f37bee25915ee26f0b440bb52cebbcd9","tid":2114592,"uid":52013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T03:07:03.000Z","msg":"1. Queen English received pronunciation.<br />\n<br />\n連登仔每個都有最正宗既英國皇室口音<br />\n如果唔係呢種口音 你只係一個鄉下仔 同大陸人無咩分別 建議你收口唔好扮野識英文<br />\n<br />\n2. Grammar-mania/nazi<br />\n<br />\nWritten English有Grammar就緊架啦<br />\n但係Conversation English都必須要遵循Grammar rule 必須先修讀Oxford Grammar book 十年先至可以係香港使用英文<br />\n<br />\n3. Guru of Intonation and meaningful English<br />\n<br />\n講野抑揚頓挫 聽到人地出耳油<br />\n媲美頂級演說家 每一句都賺人熱淚 感人肺腑 同 發人深省<br />\n<br />\n4. Various and diverse sentence structure and vocabulary range<br />\n<br />\n用字同句子都力臻完美 必須為 Formal and literary word. 絕對唔會講d通俗 常用英語  講野要出口成文 認為Williams Shakespeare都只係中學雞級數<br />\n<br />\n5. Attitude of using English in HK<br />\n<br />\n呢種心態/風氣係同輩間或網絡上 盛行一時 ---- 屌你 識講或者打中文 無啦啦學咩人講英文 以為自己好叻？懶係野<br />\n無視英語使用者背後原意同抹殺佢既努力<br />\n人地都係想培養Think in English既狀態<br />\n想捉緊每一次使用英文既機會 但熱情往往比呢d人減弱咗<br />\n<br />\n歡迎大家補充更多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T07:02:08.000Z","msg":"I concur with thee"},{"pid":"04269d57614e45bffc96bfb78e81e5a65c8e2366","tid":2114592,"uid":52013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a90c4cba845fe842558f994e65f3ad73bd52d368","tid":2114592,"uid":360830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d08987f4f37bee25915ee26f0b440bb52cebbcd9","tid":2114592,"uid":52013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T03:07:03.000Z","msg"